00:20:31.450 --> 00:20:34.320
There's universal time in
Newtonian mechanics.

00:20:34.320 --> 00:20:36.650
It just runs.
We can call some time a zero.

00:20:36.650 --> 00:20:40.234
Once we have agreed,
if you say you and I met at

00:20:40.234 --> 00:20:44.734
t = 0 and an explosion
took place 5 seconds after our

00:20:44.734 --> 00:20:47.004
meeting,
