00:23:00.512 --> 00:23:04.552
hour, you should measure the
bullet speed to be reduced by

00:23:04.552 --> 00:23:09.029
200 and you should get 400.
That's all it means.

00:23:09.029 --> 00:23:11.691
The two people will disagree on
the velocity of the bullet

00:23:11.691 --> 00:23:13.980
because they are moving relative
to each other.

00:23:13.980 --> 00:23:16.430
This is the way you will add
velocities.

00:23:16.430 --> 00:23:20.769
But let's look at the
