00:23:51.511 --> 00:23:54.894
the velocity of the body is not
changing, according to me the

00:23:54.894 --> 00:23:57.150
velocity of the body is not
changing,

00:23:57.150 --> 00:24:00.789
because the constant added will
drop out of the difference.

00:24:00.789 --> 00:24:02.972
Or, if the body has an
acceleration,

00:24:02.972 --> 00:24:06.339
